## Branch Naming Guidelines
All branches should follow the naming pattern:
<type>/<issue-number>-<short-description>

Where '<type> is one of:
- feature
- bugfix
- task
- hotfix

Example:
- 'feature/123-login'
- 'bugfix/23-headerfix'

